description: A distorted, grainy image, predominantly orange and red, features indiscernible shapes and a partially visible blue word.
The image shows a close-up of a painted surface with various abstract shapes and colors, including a blue figure resembling a person, a green plant-like shape, and some letter forms.
A woman with brown hair is speaking, and a person wearing a brown coat is partially visible.
Two young women with long hair look out of the windows of a vehicle.
A blurry close-up shot of two people's faces.
A crowd of people, some with cameras, some sitting on the ground, are gathered in front of a building with columns, with police officers standing to the right.
A blurry image shows the side of a New York City Transit Authority bus and a person inside.
A crowd of men sit and stand close together.
A blurry, slightly overexposed shot shows several people, including some press, standing near a police bus.
A man and woman are huddled close together.
A crowd of people, some wearing leather jackets and hats, are seen in what appears to be a demonstration or protest.
A blurry, washed-out image shows a large crowd of people.
A blurry, pixelated image shows people and signs, possibly in a protest or rally setting.
A blank, off-white surface with small specks of dust or debris is visible.
A group of people walk down a city street, some holding signs with a man's face on them.
Grainy footage shows several men leaning out of bus windows, waving to a crowd.
A blurry, grainy image shows part of a large painted design featuring a person or figure and faded, possibly orange and purple, colors.
A group of protesters sit on the ground facing police officers in front of a building.
A blurry, grainy close-up shows the profile of a person's face next to another person wearing a collared shirt and dark jacket.
A blurry figure interacts with a small screen or panel on a yellow wall.
A crowd of people, some wearing coats, gathers near a building with columns.
A grainy, faded photograph shows a large group of people, some sitting and some standing, in what appears to be a protest or demonstration, with several police officers in uniform present.
A blurry close-up image shows a piece of paper with the words "OUR $" and "ERE IT CAN" written on it, attached to a surface covered in various other items.
Two men in leather jackets, one facing the camera and slightly blurred, the other in profile.
A blurry, grainy image appears to show dark and light shapes against a reddish-orange background.
